actionConfiguration.body:
SELECT cr, COUNT(*)
FROM public.monsters
GROUP BY cr
ORDER BY
   CASE cr
	 		WHEN '0' THEN 0
      WHEN '1/8' THEN 1
      WHEN '1/4' THEN 2
      WHEN '1/2' THEN 3
      WHEN '1' THEN 4
			WHEN '2' THEN 5
      WHEN '3' THEN 6
      WHEN '4' THEN 7
      WHEN '5' THEN 8
			WHEN '6' THEN 9
      WHEN '7' THEN 10
      WHEN '8' THEN 11
      WHEN '9' THEN 12
			WHEN '10' THEN 13
      WHEN '11' THEN 14
      WHEN '12' THEN 15
      WHEN '13' THEN 16
			WHEN '14' THEN 17
			WHEN '15' THEN 18
      WHEN '16' THEN 19
      WHEN '17' THEN 20
      WHEN '18' THEN 21
			WHEN '19' THEN 22
      WHEN '20' THEN 23
      WHEN '21' THEN 24
      WHEN '22' THEN 25
			WHEN '23' THEN 26
			WHEN '24' THEN 27
			WHEN '25' THEN 28
      WHEN '26' THEN 29
      WHEN '27' THEN 30
      WHEN '28' THEN 31
			WHEN '29' THEN 32
      WHEN '30' THEN 33
      ELSE 34 --needed only is no IN clause above. eg when = 'b'
   END
